title: The Mysterious Madame Zola
overview: Special Agent Tanya X infiltrates a high-priced call girl ring in order to uncover a deadly nest of enemy spies. Little does she know that the deadly and dreaded ‘Madame Zola’ herself, a threat to national security is behind the organization. It is up to the super and sexy Agent Tanya X to stop Madame Zola and her international gang of spies!
